sequenceDiagram
    participant Aluno
    participant Challenge
    participant ScoringStrategy
    participant Session
    participant AchievementCenter
    participant Observer

    Aluno->>Challenge: envia submissão
    Challenge->>ScoringStrategy: calcular pontos
    ScoringStrategy-->>Challenge: retorna pontos
    Challenge->>Aluno: adiciona pontos
    Session->>Session: log_action("Aluno respondeu desafio")
    Challenge->>AchievementCenter: check_achievements(Aluno)
    AchievementCenter->>Observer: update(Aluno, Achievement)
    Observer-->>Aluno: notificação de conquista
